---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Airflow & MWAA Orchestration | Project Detail">
  <div class="project-detail-bg">
    <div class="project-detail-card">
      <a href="/projects" class="back-button">&larr; Back to Projects</a>
      <div class="project-detail-content">
        <h1>Pharma Pipeline Orchestration with Airflow & MWAA</h1>
        <p class="summary">
          Developed and maintained scalable, automated pipelines for a pharmaceutical analytics platform, utilizing Apache Airflow (MWAA) to orchestrate secure daily and historical data deliveries from de-identified master tables—enabling reliable, privacy-compliant analytics for client overlap studies.
        </p>
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Developed modular Python DAGs (Directed Acyclic Graphs) to standardize ETL tasks for all clients.</li>
          <li>Used YAML-based pipeline configuration for easy modification, scaling, and onboarding new clients and datasets.</li>
          <li>Built scheduled jobs (daily/historical) that joined de-identified claims and tokenized tables to produce analytic datasets for downstream customer research.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Infrastructure & Security</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Configured AWS IAM policies for secure, permissioned writes to client S3 buckets.</li>
          <li>Automated data shipments—leveraging Lambda Functions scheduled by AWS EventBridge—ensuring on-time, unattended delivery for all stakeholders.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Results & Value Delivered</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Enabled daily, automated, and secure data transfer for multiple pharma clients.</li>
          <li>Simplified onboarding for new engagement—no-code needed for new schedules or data splits.</li>
          <li>Reduced manual labor and improved compliance and auditability for both teams.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tech-stack-detail">
          <strong>Tech Stack:</strong>
          <span>Apache Airflow (MWAA)</span>
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>YAML</span>
          <span>AWS Lambda</span>
          <span>AWS S3</span>
          <span>EventBridge</span>
          <span>IAM Policies</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .project-detail-bg {
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.78),rgba(0,0,0,0.70)),
                  url('/images/mountain_two.jpg') no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
    .project-detail-card {
      max-width: 830px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(25, 30, 55, 0.68);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 48px 40px 52px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(130%);
    }
    .back-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-button:hover {
      color: #147bcd;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .project-detail-content {
      color: #f5f5f7;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2997ff;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .summary {
      font-size: 1.13rem;
      color: #f5f5f7;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: #79bbff;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 1.2em;
    }
    ul li {
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.2em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail {
      margin-top: 2.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
      background: rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.09);
      border-radius: 13px;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: #147bcd;
    }
    @media (max-width: 800px){
      .project-detail-card {
        padding: 20px 8px 22px 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
